OL,3,COnlyFans investigated by Ofcom over
OL,4,Cchild access concerns
OL,6,FOnlyfans is being investigated over
OL,7,Fwhether its age verification system is
OL,8,Frobust enough to prevent children from
OL,9,Faccessing pornography on the
OL,10,Fsubscription site.
OL,12,FRegulator Ofcom said it has opened
OL,13,Fformal proceedings against the UK-
OL,14,Fbased platform over concerns around
OL,15,Fthe implementation of age verification
OL,16,Fmeasures designed to protect under-18s
OL,17,Ffrom inappropriate material.
