OL,3,COnlyFans investigated by Ofcom over
OL,4,Cchild access concerns
OL,6,FUnder existing rules that pre-date the
OL,7,FUK's new Online Safety Act, video-
OL,8,Fsharing platforms established in the
OL,9,FUK are required to take appropriate
OL,10,Faction to prevent those aged under 18
OL,11,Ffrom accessing pornographic material.
OL,13,FIn response to this, OnlyFans, like
OL,14,Fother sites hosting adult content, has
OL,15,Fintroduced age verification measures.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.!/*%/"-$ /*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,
