OL,3,COnlyFans investigated by Ofcom over
OL,4,Cchild access concerns
OL,6,FHowever, Ofcom said that having
OL,7,Freviewed submissions from OnlyFans in
OL,8,Fresponse to formal information
OL,9,Frequests, it has "grounds to suspect"
OL,10,Fthe platform did not implement its age
OL,11,Fverification measures in such a way as
OL,12,Fto sufficiently protect under-18s.
OL,14,FOfcom said it is also investigating
OL,15,Fwhether the site failed to comply with
OL,16,Fits duties to provide complete and
OL,17,Faccurate information in response to
OL,18,Fthese requests.
