OL,3,COnlyFans investigated by Ofcom over
OL,4,Cchild access concerns
OL,6,FA spokesperson for OnlyFans said: "As
OL,7,Fthe leading UK-based and regulated
OL,8,Fsocial media platform, OnlyFans works
OL,9,Fclosely with Ofcom to implement and
OL,10,Fdevelop best practices on online
OL,11,Fsafety, including the use of age-
OL,12,Fassurance technology.
OL,14,F"In addition to requiring that all
OL,15,Fusers provide their name and payment
OL,16,Fcard details, OnlyFans uses the
OL,17,FGovernment-approved age assurance
OL,18,Fprovider Yoti.
