OL,3,COnlyFans investigated by Ofcom over
OL,4,Cchild access concerns
OL,6,F"A coding configuration issue with
OL,7,FYoti led to a reporting error which
OL,8,Fstated a threshold was set to 23 years
OL,9,Fof age, during a period of time when
OL,10,Fit had been set to 20 ` always higher
OL,11,Fthan the requirement of 18.
OL,13,F"OnlyFans discovered the reporting
OL,14,Ferror and proactively amended our
OL,15,Freport to Ofcom."
OL,17,FOfcom said it will provide an update
OL,18,Fon its investigation in due course.
